                                                                                                                                Messaging

                                                                                                                                Tooltip

                                                                                                                                Tooltips are brief, informative messages used to introduce new content and features or provide brief step-by-step guidance.


                                                                                                                                Tooltips usually appear for a short amount of time or in some cases, until the user dismisses them.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Content
                                                                                                                                Spec
                                                                                                                                Changelog

                                                                                                                                Metrics

                                                                                                                                On mobile, tooltips must be positioned in close proximity to the element they’re pointing to. The tooltip should be 4 px away from the parent element. They can take up no more than 50% width of the screen minus the gutters on either side.

                                                                                                                                If positioned close to any screen edge, keep a 16 px margin to ensure the tooltip does not bleed into safe areas.

                                                                                                                                Simple

                                                                                                                                With a trailing icon button

                                                                                                                                Positioning and spacing

                                                                                                                                Anchoring

                                                                                                                                All tooltips are to be displayed in a horizontal position, centered on the parent element, in order to maintain legibility and comprehension.

                                                                                                                                Don’t
                                                                                                                                Don’t have arbitrarily positioned tooltips on the screen.
                                                                                                                                Don’t
                                                                                                                                Do not randomly rotate tooltips - they are transient elements meant to be digested in a few seconds. Vertical text is not legible.

                                                                                                                                Margins

                                                                                                                                Ensure a tooltip has enough space around it and is not clashing with other elements or falling off screen.

                                                                                                                                Don’t
                                                                                                                                Do not crop or let the tooltip overflow outside of the screen bounds even if the text is legible.

                                                                                                                                Type and color tokens

                                                                                                                                Button colors

                                                                                                                                Button state colors inside tooltips are calculated programmatically. They need to be customized to work on the color token InverseBackgroundTeriary.

                                                                                                                                See button color specs on various backgrounds ->

                                                                                                                                Screen readers

                                                                                                                                VoiceOver

                                                                                                                                To voice or not to voice

                                                                                                                                Depending on the content of the tooltip and the default accessibility label of the control, voicing both might create redundancy. Group the tooltip and control in scenarios where the labels for the control = the label for the tooltip and there are no actions present inside the tooltip.

                                                                                                                                Tooltip != primary label
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                When the content inside of the Tooltip is different than the accessibility control, it needs to be voiced separately.


                                                                                                                                1. Voiced preview: "Delivery location, 1400 Broadway, Button, Double-tap to change."

                                                                                                                                Label: Delivery location

                                                                                                                                Value: 1400 Broadway

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button

                                                                                                                                Hint: Double-tap to change


                                                                                                                                2. Voiced preview: "You’re a little far away. Button. Tap to dismiss.”

                                                                                                                                Label: You’re a little far away

                                                                                                                                Value: n/a

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button

                                                                                                                                Hint: Tap to dismiss.

                                                                                                                                Tooltip = primary label
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                When the content of your Tooltip is similar or equal to the accessibility control, it is grouped with the control to avoid redundancy.


                                                                                                                                Voiced preview: "Share live location, Off, Button, Double-tap to toggle."

                                                                                                                                Label: Share live location

                                                                                                                                Value: On | Off

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button

                                                                                                                                Hint: Double-tap to toggle.

                                                                                                                                TalkBack

                                                                                                                                Tooltip = primary label
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                When the content of your Tooltip is similar or equal to the accessibility control, it is grouped with the control to avoid redundancy.


                                                                                                                                Voiced preview: "Off, Share live location, Switch, Double-tap to toggle."

                                                                                                                                ContentDescription: Share live location

                                                                                                                                Value: On | Off

                                                                                                                                Trait: Switch

                                                                                                                                Action: Double-tap to toggle

                                                                                                                                Tooltip = primary label
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                When the content inside of the Tooltip is different than the accessibility control, it needs to be voiced separately.


                                                                                                                                1. Voiced preview: "Delivery location, 1400 Broadway, Button, Double-tap to change."

                                                                                                                                ContentDescription: Delivery location, 1400 Broadway

                                                                                                                                Value: n/a

                                                                                                                                Role: Button

                                                                                                                                Action: Double-tap to change


                                                                                                                                2. Voiced preview: "You’re a little far away. Button. Double-tap to dismiss.”
